@startuml
title Engram 记忆网络 - 语义激活扩散

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

' 定义节点样式
skinparam card {
  BackgroundColor #3498DB
  FontColor white
  BorderColor #2980B9
}

' 记忆网络图
rectangle "Engram 语义网络" #ECF0F1 {

  ' 核心概念节点
  card "TypeScript" as TS #E74C3C
  card "类型系统" as Type #E74C3C
  card "接口" as Interface #F39C12
  card "泛型" as Generic #F39C12
  card "装饰器" as Decorator #F39C12

  card "React" as React #2ECC71
  card "组件" as Component #2ECC71
  card "Hooks" as Hooks #27AE60
  card "状态管理" as State #27AE60

  card "项目规范" as Spec #9B59B6
  card "命名约定" as Naming #9B59B6
  card "文件结构" as FileStruct #9B59B6

  card "性能优化" as Perf #3498DB
  card "Memo" as Memo #3498DB
  card "虚拟化" as Virtual #3498DB

  ' 连接关系
  TS -- Type : has
  Type -- Interface : includes
  Type -- Generic : includes
  TS -- Decorator : feature

  React -- Component : core
  Component -- Hooks : uses
  Hooks -- State : manages

  TS -- React : used_with
  Component -- Type : typed_by
  Interface -- Component : defines

  Spec -- Naming : includes
  Spec -- FileStruct : includes
  Naming -- Component : applies_to

  Perf -- Memo : technique
  Perf -- Virtual : technique
  Component -- Perf : optimized_by
}

' 激活扩散示意
note bottom of TS
  **激活扩散过程**

  1. 查询: "TypeScript 组件优化"
  2. 激活: TypeScript (1.0)
  3. 扩散: Type(0.8), React(0.7)
  4. 扩散: Component(0.6), Perf(0.5)
  5. 扩散: Memo(0.4), Hooks(0.3)
  6. 召回: 相关记忆片段
end note

legend right
  |= 强度 |= 含义 |
  | 1.0 | 直接激活 |
  | 0.7-0.9 | 强关联 |
  | 0.4-0.6 | 中关联 |
  | 0.1-0.3 | 弱关联 |
  | 0.0 | 未激活 |
end legend

@enduml
